{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"RFID 标签数据结构","level":2,"anchor":"RFID-%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"本库的功能都是围绕 RFID 标签而设计开发，了解一些 RFID 标签的基本信息，可以更好的去理解 RFID 相关功能"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"RFID 标签的的基本数据区域大致如下如所示："}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"RESERVED 包含 kill 和 access 两个密码数据，长度都为 32 bit，默认密码都是 00000000","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"EPC 包含三个部分：","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"crc : 循环冗余校验"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pc : epc 标签长度控制字"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"epc : 具体的 epc 用户数据"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"盘点时读取到 epc 数据长度取决于 pc 的高 5 位值，epc长度转为为pc值示例：","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"epc 长度为 6 个字 (96 bit)： 6 字 = 0011 0000 0000 0000 = 0x3000","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"epc 长度为 9 个字 (144 bit)： 9 字 = 0100 1000 0000 0000 = 0x4800","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"epc 长度为 15 个字 (240 bit)： 15 字 = 0111 1000 0000 0000 = 0x7800","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TID 区域均为 tid 数据。一般来说，tid 长度为 96 bit, 是唯一且无法修改的","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"USER 区域均为 user 数据，其长度取决于具体标签，不同类型标签的 USER 区域容量可能不同","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"这篇文章主要介绍一些 RFID 相关的基本知识，方便你能更好的了解 RFIDManager 库"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"RFIDManager"}],"title":"RFID 基本知识"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/doc